{"tid":2150433,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"工程繪圖畫板？","createTime":"2020-08-11T02:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T01:47:14.000Z","uid":209453,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3c541273cea6031e45a8c7242e749df47dc031","tid":2150433,"uid":209453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n屋企人做機械工程，一直都係手畫圖。AutoCad都唔識用。<br />\n最新想嘗試用電子繪畫板畫圖。<br />\n<br />\n1. 係未大部分有螢幕嘅畫板都做到同電腦同步畫面？<br />\n2. AutoCad支唔支援畫板？<br />\n3. 有無其他程式係畫板支援，做到繪圖後，可於線條嘅設定隨時改變線條長度或弧度？ 重有鎖點拉線及標示尺寸嘅功能。"},{"pid":"7b7a9306ef9673913c27501eea289a15a984b3df","tid":2150433,"uid":276273,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"AutoCAD 用繪圖板咪玩死自己，咪咁傻啦"},{"pid":"d39a918c4ffadca12fe69f89bc7f0a863773a2b3","tid":2150433,"uid":209453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b7a9306ef9673913c27501eea289a15a984b3df","tid":2150433,"uid":276273,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"AutoCAD 用繪圖板咪玩死自己，咪咁傻啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"有程式可以係畫板做到拉直線，拉弧線，標尺寸，改長度都夠。<br />\n試咗幾種，都係畫線，而唔係拉線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a657212ef2853c6cdb0e90d0d591feb021fa011","tid":2150433,"uid":29689,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"學autocad 應該仲快過你搵到塊啱用嘅繪圖板/app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915cf9b835c63ac651a29d5ece968ee389da4691","tid":2150433,"uid":326897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"你講哩啲?<br />\n除咗地政重會用嚟張紙圖數碼化嗰陣用，<br />\n應該冇乜人用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fE7DqpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfE7DqpS.jpg&h=b5a23e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係哩啲? <br />\n你唔係做平版cg跟本冇用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGAUJcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGAUJcG.jpg&h=11516dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如好好地去學autocad/bim 好過"},{"pid":"f59bed914c9321cf0ae35244af71068bbb178ad4","tid":2150433,"uid":326897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"e&amp;m 嘅應該係去學 pro e，<br />\ninventor，solidwork，<br />\n嗰啲唔會用數位版，<br />\n嗰啲會用mouse 加 3d space navigator<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3RAhF39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3RAhF39.png&h=c90910d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dafe1bc9ce3556933074af2a3478927c9d3d80f","tid":2150433,"uid":209453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECLmowU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECLmowU.png&h=eabff532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依張手畫，想轉用畫板畫。<br />\n本身諗住畫板拉直線會快過用手，用間尺畫；<br />\n想改尺寸又唔洗重新畫過。<br />\n<br />\n試咗好多程式都係俾人畫畫，而唔係拉線，標尺寸。"},{"pid":"36ada2f283d179445e94da5ef96621a9426f023e","tid":2150433,"uid":209453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dafe1bc9ce3556933074af2a3478927c9d3d80f","tid":2150433,"uid":209453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECLmowU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECLmowU.png&h=eabff532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依張手畫，想轉用畫板畫。<br />\n本身諗住畫板拉直線會快過用手，用間尺畫；<br />\n想改尺寸又唔洗重新畫過。<br />\n<br />\n試咗好多程式都係俾人畫畫，而唔係拉線，標尺寸。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"用Ipad上嘅&rdquo;Shapr 3D 建模CAD&rdquo; 最接近我想做嘅嘢。<br />\n不過唔知有無其他選擇。"},{"pid":"2d8a13d4630bd5a4d0d3b0367686d3a750301fcf","tid":2150433,"uid":326897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5dafe1bc9ce3556933074af2a3478927c9d3d80f","tid":2150433,"uid":209453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECLmowU.png\" data-thum